TIER UPDATE LOGIC (MONTHLY BASIS):
```
Current Month Orders â†’ Action:

TIER 1:
- If orders >= 10 â†’ UPGRADE to Tier 2
- Else â†’ MAINTAIN Tier 1

TIER 2:
- If orders >= 25 â†’ UPGRADE to Tier 3
- Else if orders < 10 â†’ DOWNGRADE to Tier 1
- Else â†’ MAINTAIN Tier 2

TIER 3:
- If orders >= 75 â†’ UPGRADE to Tier MAX
- Else if orders < 25 â†’ DOWNGRADE to Tier 2
- Else â†’ MAINTAIN Tier 3

TIER MAX:
- If orders < 75 â†’ DOWNGRADE to Tier 3
- Else â†’ MAINTAIN Tier MAX
```

Requirements:
- Count orders by month/year
- Use tier constants yang BARU
- Send email notification on change
- Max 200 lines

